quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  114,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  114,1,kaho ke mein logon ke perwar-digaar ki panah mangta hon
  114,2,( yani ) logon ke haqeeqi badshah ki
  114,3,logon ke mabood barhaq ki
  114,4,( shetan ) waswasa andaaz ki buraiee se jo ( khuda ka naam sun kar ) peechay hatt jata hai
  114,5,jo logon ke dilon mein was wasay dalta hai
  114,6,woh jinnaat mein se ( ho ) ya insanon mein se
